Description:
Gran Turismo 6 - continuation of the famous series autosimulators created on a new engine . Initially, the game features 1,200 cars , the amount of which is replenished through the DLC, as well as 33 locations . The existing tracks added seven brand new , including the Silverstone circuit , where the celebration of the fifteenth anniversary of the series.
The new engine provides updated system rendering physics suspension , tire adhesion to the road surface and revised aerodynamic model . The new editor allows you to create your own tracks and championships customize tournaments . Updated interface has become much easier , and download time significantly decreased.
